Eversept Global Healthcare Fund Form D
The New York-based Eversept Global Healthcare Fund, Lp had published D form regarding $17.49 million offering. The date of first sale was 2011-03-21. The Limited Partnership raised $17.49 million. The offering is still open. The total offering amount was $17.49 million. The private offering document was filed on 2015-12-01. Eversept Global Healthcare Fund, Lp’s clarification was: Customary advisory fees are paid by the Issuer to the Investment Manager as provided for in the Issuer’s offering materials.. 
 Eversept Global Healthcare Fund is based in New York. The filler’s business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was submitted by Kamran Moghtaderi Managing Member of the General Partner. The company was incorporated in 2011. The filler’s address is: 1745 Broadway, 24Th Floor, New York, Ny, New York, 10019. – Eversept Gp, Llc is the related person in the form and it has address: 1745 Broadway, 24Th Floor, New York, Ny, New York, 10019. Link to Eversept Global Healthcare Fund Filing: 000151660615000002.
Analysis of Eversept Global Healthcare Fund Offering
On average, companies in the Pooled Investment Fund sector, sell 37.80 % investment fund interests. Eversept Global Healthcare Fund sold 100.00 % of the offering. The average investment size is $24.76 million for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund industry sector. The total amount raised is 29.34 % smaller than the average for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund sector. 

